OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-Camelot boss named as   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnew Post Office chairman   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The former boss of Camelot has been    
OL,6, confirmed as interim chairman of the   
OL,7, Post Office after its last leader was  
OL,8, sacked.                                
OL,10,FNigel Railton has been appointed by    
OL,11,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch after 
OL,12,FHenry Staunton departed in January.    
OL,14,FHe takes on the role as hundreds of    
OL,15,Fsub-postmasters are still waiting for  
OL,16,Fcompensation over the Horizon scandal. 
OL,18,FMr Railton spent 24 years at former    
OL,19,FNational Lottery operator Camelot UK   
OL,20,Fbefore stepping down last year.        
